# Phinny dev environment. Copy to .env (gitignored) and fill in.
#
# SimpleFIN setup token for local development. When set, a Debug build launched
# via ./scripts/run.sh auto-connects to your real account on first launch
# (instead of showing demo data). The token is single-use: after the first
# connect the access URL is stored in your Keychain and this value is ignored.
#
# Get one at simplefin.org -> My Account -> New SimpleFIN Setup Token.
# NOTE: connecting performs one real sync (counts against ~24/day).
SIMPLEFIN_TOKEN=
